vative software and product delivery Without the requirement to write code, lead our development from the front, ensuring productivity, transparency and plannability Ensure continuous service delivery with attention to information security, scalability, and business continuity at all times. Manage the development, release and ongoing operation of future product initiatives. Desired Skills: Confident and self-motivated, comfortable within an SME, you\u2019ll have an excellent leadership style with the ability to quickly build strong working relationships. Exceptional communication, organisation and problem-solving skills are also key, as is the ability to effectively prioritise your workload You will have a broad understanding of the technology landscape, able to select and deploy the most effective solution. An open and honest approach with a high degree of ethical integrity. An empathy with environmental issues and desire to take positive action. Benefits and other information: Be part of a growing innovative business and help shape the future of energy Collaborative, flexible and friendly environment Bespoke personal development budget Normal working hours are 9 am to 5:30 pm Guru Systems will match 5% pension contributions 25 days holiday 2 Volunteer / Social Engagement Days Quarterly and annual social events, from bowling to a whole company getaway We offer great perks and discounts with free access to health and wellness support and more. Free coffee, teas and fruit every day, and a variety of beverages on a Friday! More about Guru: We have brought together a fantastic team of extremely bright people from fields that don\u2019t usually overlap: energy, engineering, IoT, software development and Big Data analytics. Proud of our award-winning team and products, we maintain high standards, certified to ISO9001, ISO14001, ISO27001 and Cyber Essentials Plus. We provide an open and supportive environment to ensure that together our success continues to grow.?We encourage diversity and seek out unique points of view. We embrace innovation and stretch to achieve great things. Oh, and we are located in a fantastic sustainable office close to Borough Market. To apply - hit the button above. ",
